#

Easy Tofu and Broccoli Stir-Fry

25 min
$8
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyStir-Fry

Description

A quick and healthy stir-fry with protein-rich tofu and crisp broccoli, tossed in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • sesame oil: 1 tsp
  • salt and pepper: to taste
